S063C.Q1. WHAT IS YOUR ARMY RANK OR GRADE?  1. PRIVATE 2. PRIVATE FIRST CLASS 3. TECHNICIAN 5TH GRADE OR CORPORAL 4. TECHNICIAN 4TH GRADE OR SERGEANT 5. TECHNICIAN 3RD GRADE OR STAFF SERGEANT 6. TECHNICAL SERGEANT 7. MASTER SERGEANT OR FIRST SERGEANT 0. NO ANSWER
S063C.Q2. HOW OLD WERE YOU ON YOUR LAST BIRTHDAY?  01. 18 YEARS OR YOUNGER 02. 19 YEARS 03. 20 04. 21 05. 22 06. 23 07. 24 08. 25 09. 26-29 YEARS 10. 30-34 YEARS 11. 35 YEARS AND OVER 00. NO ANSWER

S063C.Q5. WHERE WERE YOU LIVING MOST OF THE LAST FIVE YEARS OF YOUR CIVILIAN LIFE BEFORE YOU CAME INTO THE ARMY?  1. ON A FARM OR IN THE COUNTRY 2. IN A SMALL TOWN (FEWER THAN 2,500 PEOPLE) 3. IN A TOWN (WITH BETWEEN 2,500 AND 25,000 PEOPLE) 4. IN A CITY (BETWEEN 25,000 AND 100,000 PEOPLE) 5. IN A LARGE CITY (MORE THAN 100,000 PEOPLE) 6. NO ANSWER 0. NO CODE OR NO DATA X. S063C.Q11. HOW LONG HAVE YOU BEEN IN THE ARMY? E. IF YOU HAVE BEEN IN THE ARMY BEFORE, THEN WERE OUT FOR A WHILE, JUST CHECK THE LENGTH OF TIME SINCE YOU ENTERED THIS LAST TIME. IF YOU WERE IN THE NATIONAL GUARD, CHECK THE LENGTH OF TIME SINCE YOUR OUTFIT CAME INTO THE ARMY.  1. 3 MONTHS OR LESS 2. OVER 3 MONTHS UP TO 6 MONTHS 3. OVER 6 MONTHS UP TO 9 MONTHS 4. OVER 9 MONTHS UP TO 1 YEAR 5. OVER 1 YEAR UP TO 2 YEARS 6. OVER 2 YEARS 0. NO ANSWER

S063C.Q12. HAS THE ARMY CLASSIFIED YOU AS A LIMITED SERVICE MAN?  1. YES, THE ARMY HAS CLASSIFIED ME AS LIMITED SERVICE 2. NO, THE ARMY HAS NOT CLASSIFIED ME AS LIMITED SERVICE 3. I DON'T KNOW WHETHER THE ARMY HAS CLASSIFIED ME AS LIMITED SERVICE OR NOT 0. NO ANSWER X. QUESTION 13 NOT CODED.
S063C.Q14. WHAT KIND OF WORK WOULD YOU LIKE TO DO AFTER THE WAR?  1. SAME AS I DID BEFORE ENTERING THE ARMY 2. SOME OTHER KIND OF WORK 3. UNDECIDED 0. NO ANSWER

S063C.Q15. HOW MANY YEARS WAS IT BETWEEN THE TIME YOU LEFT FULL-TIME SCHOOL AND THE TIME YOU CAME INTO THE ARMY?  1. 1 YEAR OR LESS 2. OVER 1 YEAR UP TO 2 YEARS 3. OVER 2 YEARS UP TO 3 YEARS 4. OVER 3 YEARS UP TO 4 YEARS 5. OVER 4 YEARS UP TO 5 YEARS 6. OVER 5 YEARS 7. I CAME INTO THE ARMY RIGHT OUT OF SCHOOL 0. NO ANSWER

S063C.Q17A. REGARDLESS OF WHAT YOU WANT TO DO, DO YOU THINK YOU WILL ACTUALLY GO BACK TO FULL-TIME SCHOOL OR COLLEGE AFTER THE WAR?  1. YES 2. NO 3. UNDECIDED 0. NO ANSWER X. QUESTIONS 17B AND 18 NOT CODED.

S063C.Q25. WOULD YOU CHANGE TO SOME OTHER ARMY JOB IF GIVEN A CHANCE?  1. YES 2. NO 3. UNDECIDED 0. NO ANSWER

S063C.Q28. IN GENERAL, WHAT SORT OF A TIME DO YOU HAVE IN THE ARMY?  1. I HAVE A PRETTY GOOD TIME 2. IT'S ABOUT FIFTY-FIFTY 3. I HAVE A PRETTY ROTTEN TIME 4. NO ANSWER 0. NO CODE OR NO DATA

S063C.Q29. IN GENERAL, HOW WOULD YOU SAY YOU FEEL MOST OF THE TIME, IN GOOD SPIRITS OR IN LOW SPIRITS?  1. I AM USUALLY IN GOOD SPIRITS 2. I AM IN GOOD SPIRITS SOME OF THE TIME AND IN LOW SPIRITS SOME OF THE TIME 3. I AM USUALLY IN LOW SPIRITS 0. NO ANSWER
S063C.Q30. ARE YOU EVER WORRIED AND UPSET?  1. I AM HARDLY EVER WORRIED AND UPSET 2. I AM SOMETIMES WORRIED AND UPSET 3. I AM OFTEN WORRIED AND UPSET 0. NO ANSWER

S063C.Q31. IF IT WERE UP TO YOU, WHAT KIND OF OUTFIT WOULD YOU RATHER BE IN?  1. IN A COMBAT OUTFIT OVERSEAS 2. IN A NON-COMBAT OUTFIT OVERSEAS 3. IN AN OUTFIT THAT WILL STAY IN THE UNITED STATES 0. NO ANSWER
S063C.Q32. IF IT WERE UP TO YOU TO CHOOSE, DO YOU THINK YOU COULD DO MORE FOR YOUR COUNTRY AS A SOLDIER OR AS A WORKER IN A WAR JOB?  1. AS A SOLDIER 2. AS A WAR WORKER 3. UNDECIDED 0. NO ANSWER
S063C.Q33. DO YOU HAVE TROUBLE FINDING INTERESTING THINGS TO DO IN YOUR OFF-DUTY FREE TIME?  1. MOST OF THE TIME 2. MUCH OF THE TIME 3. NOT VERY OFTEN 4. NEVER 0. NO ANSWER

YES, TWICE 3. YES, THREE OR FOUR TIMES 4. YES, ALMOST EVERY DAY 5. NO, NO SPORTS OR ATHLETIC GAMES DURING TRAINING OR DUTY HOURS 6. DON'T KNOW 0. NO ANSWER

DO YOU YOURSELF USUALLY TAKE PART IN THIS REGULAR PROGRAM OF OFF-DUTY SPORTS OR ATHLETIC GAMES?  1. YES, OFF-DUTY PROGRAM - YES, USUALLY TAKE PART 2. YES, OFF-DUTY PROGRAM - NO, DO NOT USUALLY TAKE PART 3. YES, OFF-DUTY PROGRAM, NO ANSWER TO Q.38B 4. NO, THERE IS NO OFF-DUTY ATHLETIC PROGRAM IN WHICH THE MEN IN MY OUTFIT CAN TAKE PART 5. DON'T KNOW IF THERE IS AN OFF-DUTY ATHLETIC PROGRAM 0. NO ANSWER
